{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#12325: 组件无法正确解析 v-bind=\"toRefs(props)\"",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:21:49.334995+00:00",
  "text": "组件无法正确解析 v-bind=\"toRefs(props)\"\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3.5.3\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e357d852-720e-49d4-bec2-19d9b546a0dd)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n我并不清楚这是否是一个 bug，还是说这么处理是官方有意为之。如果是官方默认行为，我创建了一个讨论，并希望官方能进行支持。这一行为是符合直觉的。\r\n\r\n[props 传递过程中支持解构 refs](https://github.com/orgs/vuejs/discussions/12324)\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\nno response\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
